{"data":[{"name":"101:1","price":"衝撃¹、","arabic":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6158,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「衝撃」とは、その恐怖と戦慄（せんりつ）によって創造物に衝撃を与える、復活の日*のこと（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１６４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-qāriʿatu ","translations":["The Striking Calamity","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["al-qāriʿatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2245]]}},{"name":"101:2","price":"衝撃とは何か？","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6159,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā al-qāriʿatu ","translations":["What","(is) the Striking Calamity","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","al-qāriʿatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,240],[2,240,2215]]}},{"name":"101:3","price":"衝撃とは何かを、何があなたに知らせるか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6160,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-qāriʿatu ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","(is) the Striking Calamity","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-qāriʿatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2189],[2,2189,3639],[3,3639,3759],[4,3759,5464]]}},{"name":"101:4","price":"（衝撃とは、）人々が散り散りになった蛾のようになり、¹","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6161,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　その数の多さ、哀（あわ）れさと、散らばり、混乱した様子が蛾に譬（たと）えられている（アル＝バイダーウィー５：５２２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yakūnu al-nāsu kal-farāshi al-mabthūthi ","translations":["(The) Day","will be","the mankind","like moths","scattered","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yakūnu","al-nāsu","kal-farāshi","al-mabthūthi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,1580],[3,1580,3150],[4,3150,4470],[5,4470,7355]]}},{"name":"101:5","price":"また山々が、梳かれた羊毛のようになる日。¹","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6162,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"復活の日*の山々の変化については、洞窟章４７の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"watakūnu al-jibālu kal-ʿih'ni al-manfūshi ","translations":["And will be","the mountains","like wool","fluffed up","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["watakūnu","al-jibālu","kal-ʿih'ni","al-manfūshi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2270],[3,2270,3360],[4,3360,7535]]}},{"name":"101:6","price":"自分の（善行の）秤が（悪行の秤より）重かった者はといえば、¹","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6163,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"復活の日*の秤については、高壁章８の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man thaqulat mawāzīnuhu ","translations":["Then as for","(him) whose","(are) heavy","his scales","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","thaqulat","mawāzīnuhu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,2970],[3,2970,3900],[4,3900,5655]]}},{"name":"101:7","price":"彼は（天国で）満足な生活の中にある。","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6164,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fahuwa fī ʿīshatin rāḍiyatin ","translations":["Then he","(will be) in","a life","pleasant","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fahuwa","fī","ʿīshatin","rāḍiyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1160],[3,1160,2240],[4,2240,3785]]}},{"name":"101:8","price":"また、自分の（善行の）秤が（悪行の秤より）軽かった者はといえば、","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6165,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man khaffat mawāzīnuhu ","translations":["But as for","(him) whose","(are) light","his scales","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","khaffat","mawāzīnuhu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1900],[2,1900,2270],[3,2270,3160],[4,3160,4945]]}},{"name":"101:9","price":"その落ち着く先は、墜落。¹","arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6166,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"「落ち着く先（ウンム）」には、「頭」という解釈もある。その場合、「頭から業火へと墜落する」という意味となる。また、「墜落」とは、底知れず墜落する場所である、地獄の別称（アル＝バガウィー５：２９７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ummuhu hāwiyatun ","translations":["His abode","(will be the) Pit","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ummuhu","hāwiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,3335]]}},{"name":"101:10","price":"それが何かを、何があなたに知らせるか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6167,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā hiyah ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","it is","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","hiyah",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,3060],[3,3060,3480],[4,3480,4415]]}},{"name":"101:11","price":"（それは）酷熱の業火である。","arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6168,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"nārun ḥāmiyatun ","translations":["A Fire","intensely hot","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["nārun","ḥāmiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2500],[2,2500,4435]]}}],"chapter":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah","Chapter Al-Qari'ah","Qari'ah","Surah Qari'ah","Chapter Qari'ah","Al Qari'ah","Surah Al Qari'ah","Chapter Al Qari'ah","Surah 101","Chapter 101","The Calamity","القارعة"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}